headline: Tracking the Narrative for Jack Henry as Growth Catalysts and Caution Shift the Outlook
summary: Jack Henry & Associates’ stock price target has inched up, with the fair value estimate rising slightly from $179.17 to $181.23 per share. This modest increase reflects analyst optimism around new contract wins and industry trends, even as some caution remains amid broader sector volatility.
